stars or more complex events\nthat occur during the epoch of planet formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2022 16:34:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Aug 2022 15:34:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-23"}
