, which eludes to the potential of the technique and highlights that a\nUAV-based system is a viable calibration technique for current and future\nground-based $\\gamma$-ray telescope arrays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2022 10:33:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-01"}
