ated to verify the model's calibration. The application of the\nproposed MUD scheme is investigated in an indoor factory setting using four\ndifferent mmWave channel models. Numerical results show that when the number of\nactive MTDs in the system is large, the proposed MUD has a significantly higher\nprobability of detection compared to existing approaches over the\nsignal-to-noise ratio range of interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2022 11:25:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 May 2023 15:05:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-01"}
